<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Đăng nhập</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.8.2/css/all.css"
        integrity="sha384-oS3vJWv+0UjzBfQzYUhtDYW+Pj2yciDJxpsK1OYPAYjqT085Qq/1cq5FLXAZQ7Ay" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/views/resources/css/Login-page.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="template">
        <header class="header-style">
            <label class="label-click" id="label-click"><i class="fas fa-list-ul"></i></label>
            <div class="Logo">
                <a href=""><img class="Logo-img" src="/views/resources/image/Logo.png" alt="Logo"></a>
            </div>
            <div class="function-name">
                <a href="/homepage"> Trang chủ</a>
            </div>
            <div class="regularly-action" id="regularly-action">
                <a > <span><i class="fas fa-user" style="margin-right: 5px"></i></span> Đăng nhập</a>
            </div>
        </header>
        <div class="Left" id="Left">
            <div class="home-page">
                <a href="/homepage"> <span><i class="fas fa-home"></i></span> <span id="span1"> Trang chủ </span></a>
            </div>
            <div class="About" >
                <p class="pAbout" id="pAbout"> <span><i class="fas fa-question"></i></span> <span id="span3">Thông tin thêm</span> </p>
                <ul id="hideOrShow" style="display: none">
                    <li>Các chức năng được sử dụng khi bạn đã đăng nhập</li>
                    <li>Khi đăng nhập lần đầu: bạn sử dụng tên đăng nhập và mật khẩu là mã đăng nhập</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <nav>
            <div class="work-area">
                <div>
                    <form id="formLogin" action="/login-confirm" method="POST">
                        <div class="smLog">Đăng nhập</div>
                        <p id="pAlert">Bạn chưa nhập tên đăng nhập, mật khẩu</p>
                        <div class="clearfix"></div>
                        <div class="smAcc">
                            <p class="inputText"><span class="input_icn"><i class="fas fa-user-alt"></i></span><input
                                    style="border:none" type="text" name="username" id="uname"
                                    placeholder="Tên đăng nhập" maxlength="30" tabindex="1"></p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="clearfix"></div>
                        <div class="smPass">
                            <p class="passText"><span class="pass_icn"><i class="fas fa-lock"></i></span><input
                                    style="border:none" type="password" name="password" id="pass" placeholder="Mật khẩu"
                                    maxlength="30" tabindex="2"></p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="clearfix"></div>
                        <p> <span class="eyes" id="eyes"><i class="fas fa-eye"></i>Hiển thị mật khẩu</span> <button type="submit" class="submitBtn" id="submitBtn"> ĐĂNG NHẬP </button></p>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </div>
</body>
<script src="/views/resources/js/Login-page.js"></script>

</html>